程序包 org.cloudbus.cloudsim.lists

类 PeList

java.lang.Object
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.lists.PeList
public class PeList
extends java.lang.Object
PeList is a collection of operations on lists of PEs.
从以下版本开始:
CloudSim Toolkit 2.0

      返回:
      the PE with the given id or null if not found

      返回:

    • setPeStatus

      public static <T extends Pe> boolean setPeStatus​(java.util.List<T> peList, int id, int status)
      Sets a PE status.
      参数:
      status - the PE status, either Pe.FREE or Pe.BUSY
      id - the id of the PE to be set
      peList - the PE list
      返回:
      true if the PE status has been changed, false otherwise (PE id might not be exist)

    • setStatusFailed

      public static <T extends Pe> void setStatusFailed​(java.util.List<T> peList, java.lang.String resName, int hostId, boolean failed)
      Sets the status of PEs of a host to FAILED or FREE. NOTE: resName and hostId are used for debugging purposes, which is ON by default. Use #setStatusFailed(boolean) if you do not want this information.
      参数:
      peList - the host's PE list to be set as failed or free
      resName - the name of the resource
      hostId - the id of the host
      failed - true if the host's PEs have to be set as FAILED, false if they have to be set as FREE.
      另请参阅:
      setStatusFailed(java.util.List, boolean)

    • setStatusFailed

      public static <T extends Pe> void setStatusFailed​(java.util.List<T> peList, boolean failed)
      Sets the status of PEs of a host to FAILED or FREE.
      参数:
      peList - the host's PE list to be set as failed or free
      failed - true if the host's PEs have to be set as FAILED, false if they have to be set as FREE.
